A nasty war has broken out between SABC soccer analyst David Kekana and his estranged sugar mama over the division of their estate and control of their company. Sunday World can reveal that Kekana's wife, Lesley Jane Kekana, had applied for an order in the Joburg high court to force him to hand over share certificates of trust accounts he allegedly took when vacating their multimillion- rand home in Dainfern Estate, north of Joburg. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD